{"tid":332701,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警務處舉行夏季招募日，有超過2600人投考","createTime":"2017-07-23T07:56:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-23T10:36:55.000Z","uid":12609,"like":3,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7396a6c68db2de5302465e14ffeed0aeb40840d2","tid":332701,"uid":12609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T07:56:18.000Z","msg":"夏季招募日在灣仔警察總部舉行，警方先為投考人士進行初步遴選。<br />\n<br />\n警方今個財政年度計劃招募1800多人，包括見習督察及警員，總共收到超過2600份申請，較去年同期升百分之3.4，其中投考警員人數是2010年以來最多。<br />\n<br />\n有申請人表示：「朋友、老師都說，我是比較陽光的類型，如果我成為警察，我相信我和市民溝通和相處，應該不會有特別問題。」<br />\n<br />\n亦有申請人說：「比起九十年代槍彈雨林的情況，其實現在香港治安很好，與市民接觸，都是警隊的工作。」<br />\n<br />\n警方表示會考慮申請人的溝通技巧、危機應變等能力，價值觀是否與警方相近。<br />\n<br />\n署理警察招募組警司郭志濠指：「考生的政治立場，不是我們其中一個考慮因素，我們可能會問他對社會事件，有沒有了解。因為我們相信作為前線警務人員，要服務好市民，對身邊發生的事一定要有良好觸覺。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/23/155525_1e7926e6fa70c149930c844df48e7add.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F23%2F155525_1e7926e6fa70c149930c844df48e7add.jpg&h=3e956d58&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.tvb.com/local/5972edc46db28c950eff0b17/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.tvb.com%2Flocal%2F5972edc46db28c950eff0b17%2F&d=5n9YH7FGFU9NqkzafQ4k2wRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=ce81e49c\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.tvb.com/local/5972edc46db28c950eff0b17/</a>"},{"pid":"7deeab9a68270d315a465bf5809603c14c59c7cf","tid":332701,"uid":9193,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T07:57:16.000Z","msg":"陽光到頭髮都冇晒"},{"pid":"305ff511209cc62c40b5fa07821316448a89fce5","tid":332701,"uid":56459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T07:57:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>夏季招募日在灣仔警察總部舉行，警方先為投考人士進行初步遴選。<br />\n<br />\n警方今個財政年度計劃招募1800多人，包括見習督察及警員，總共收到超過2600份申請，較去年同期升百分之3.4，其中投考警員人數是2010年以來最多。<br />\n<br />\n有申請人表示：「朋友、老師都說，我是比較陽光的類型，如果我成為警察，我相信我和市民溝通和相處，應該不會有特別問題。」<br />\n<br />\n亦有申請人說：「比起九十年代槍彈雨林的情況，其實現在香港治安很好，與市民接觸，都是警隊的工作。」<br />\n<br />\n警方表示會考慮申請人的溝通技巧、危機應變等能力，價值觀是否與警方相近。<br />\n<br />\n署理警察招募組警司郭志濠指：「考生的政治立場，不是我們其中一個考慮因素，我們可能會問他對社會事件，有沒有了解。因為我們相信作為前線警務人員，要服務好市民，對身邊發生的事一定要有良好觸覺。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/23/155525_1e7926e6fa70c149930c844df48e7add.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F23%2F155525_1e7926e6fa70c149930c844df48e7add.jpg&h=3e956d58&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.tvb.com/local/5972edc46db28c950eff0b17/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.tvb.com%2Flocal%2F5972edc46db28c950eff0b17%2F&d=5n9YH7FGFU9NqkzafQ4k2wRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=ce81e49c\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.tvb.com/local/5972edc46db28c950eff0b17/</a></blockquote><br />\n未來處長 禿鷹"},{"pid":"37802f3592518ec89528de4e74431f8b686f7f5d","tid":332701,"uid":65128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T08:06:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f188301a63690bd442e76f70f89dc8811d4ee018","tid":332701,"uid":102096,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T08:09:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"88350b4d4d6d3dbd7545969a822437d9f761574c","tid":332701,"uid":23682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T10:23:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實有唔少係為捉賊除暴安良</blockquote><br />\n更多係為咗份糧"},{"pid":"a84017a5acc922d0cb13cf12ed9bc72df00c809c","tid":332701,"uid":550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T10:27:37.000Z","msg":"咁毒都去考警察<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\